<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Context Grammar — A design language for the post-app era</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Google+Sans:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700&family=Google+Sans+Text:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Google+Sans:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');</style>
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --bg: #ffffff;
  --bg-warm: #fafaf8;
  --bg-cool: #f4f4f2;
  --bg-dark: #111113;
  --text: #18181b;
  --text-2: #52525b;
  --text-3: #a1a1aa;
  --border: #e4e4e7;
  --accent: #2563eb;
  --red: #dc2626;
  --green: #16a34a;
  --amber: #d97706;
  --font: 'Google Sans', 'Google Sans Text', -apple-system, sans-serif;
  --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  --max-w: min(1200px, 90vw);
  --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}

html {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  font-size: clamp(16px, 1.1vw, 20px);
}
body { overflow-x: hidden; }

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE SECTIONS — Full viewport slides
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
.phase {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: clamp(80px, 10vw, 140px) clamp(32px, 6vw, 100px);
  position: relative;
}

.phase-inner {
  max-width: min(1200px, 90vw);
  width: 100%;
}

/* ═══ ANIMATIONS ═══ */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1),
              transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.d1 { transition-delay: 0.12s; }
.d2 { transition-delay: 0.24s; }
.d3 { transition-delay: 0.36s; }
.d4 { transition-delay: 0.48s; }
.d5 { transition-delay: 0.60s; }
.d6 { transition-delay: 0.72s; }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes bob {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%     { transform: translateY(10px); }
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%,100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%     { opacity: 0.4; }
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 0 — HERO
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#hero {
  background: var(--bg-dark);
  color: #fff;
  flex-direction: column;
  text-align: center;
}
.hero-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.9vw, 14px);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s forwards;
}
.hero-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 80px);
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -3px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.5s forwards;
}
.hero-title em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 22px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin: 0 auto 56px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.7s forwards;
}
.scroll-cue {
  display: inline-flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.2s forwards;
}
.scroll-cue-line {
  width: 1px; height: 48px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.25), transparent);
  animation: bob 2.8s 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 1 — THE GAP
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#gap { background: var(--bg); }
.gap-section-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  text-align: center;
}
.gap-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 64px);
  align-items: start;
}
@media (max-width: 800px) {
  .gap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .gap-divider-v { display: none; }
}
.gap-col-title {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.gap-knows .gap-col-title { color: var(--green); }
.gap-misses .gap-col-title { color: var(--accent); }
.gap-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  padding: 8px 0;
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.15vw, 18px);
  font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.gap-item .gi-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.gap-knows .gi-dot { background: var(--green); }
.gap-misses .gi-dot { background: var(--accent); }
.gap-misses .gap-item { color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }
.gap-divider-v {
  width: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  align-self: stretch;
  margin: 48px 0;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 2 — INTENT-CENTERED FRAMEWORK
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#framework { background: var(--bg-cool); }
.fw-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.fw-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 52px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -2px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.fw-sub {
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 18px);
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 580px;
  margin-bottom: 56px;
}

/* ── Intent Hub ── */
.intent-hub {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 880px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Center intent node */
.intent-center {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.intent-center-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-3);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.intent-center-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(24px, 2.8vw, 40px);
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.intent-center-title em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 300;
}
.intent-center-sub {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1vw, 16px);
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Dimension cards grid */
.dim-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
}
@media (max-width: 800px) {
  .dim-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .dim-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

.dim-card {
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.35s var(--ease);
  text-align: left;
  position: relative;
}
.dim-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(37,99,235,0.08);
}
.dim-card-question {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.1vw, 17px);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.35;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.dim-card-name {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.8vw, 13px);
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}
.dim-card-examples {
  margin-top: 8px;
  font-size: clamp(12px, 0.85vw, 14px);
  color: var(--text-3);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* Connector lines (subtle) */
.intent-connector {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.intent-connector-line {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 2px;
  height: 24px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--border));
  border-radius: 1px;
}
.intent-connector-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-3);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  display: block;
  margin-top: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.fw-explore-hint {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(12px, 0.9vw, 14px);
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 3 — TOKEN EXPLORER (Horizontal)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#explorer {
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding: 0;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: var(--bg);
}

/* Top nav bar with tabs */
.te-nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 50;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 clamp(24px, 4vw, 64px);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  height: 56px;
  gap: 0;
  overflow-x: auto;
  scrollbar-width: none;
}
.te-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

.te-tab {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  padding: 16px clamp(10px, 1.2vw, 16px);
  font-size: clamp(13px, 0.95vw, 15px);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--text-3);
  cursor: pointer;
  border: none;
  background: none;
  font-family: var(--font);
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.25s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.te-tab:hover { color: var(--text-2); }
.te-tab.active {
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 600;
  border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
}
.te-tab-num {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  margin-right: 6px;
  opacity: 0.5;
}
@media (max-width: 1512px) {
  .te-tab {
    padding: 14px clamp(8px, 1vw, 14px);
    font-size: clamp(12px, 0.9vw, 14px);
  }
  .te-tab-num {
    display: none;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 1200px) {
  .te-tab {
    padding: 12px 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
}

.te-progress {
  margin-left: auto;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  color: var(--text-3);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  padding: 0 8px;
}

/* Slide container */
.te-slides {
  flex: 1;
  position: relative;
}

.te-slide {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: stretch;
  padding: 0;
  min-height: calc(100vh - 56px);
  animation: slideIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.te-slide.active { display: flex; }

@keyframes slideIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Left side: illustration in cool background */
.te-slide > .ts-illustration {
  flex: 0 0 42%;
  background: var(--bg-cool);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px);
}

/* Right side: content wrapper */
.te-slide > *:not(.ts-illustration) {
  flex: 1 1 58%;
}

/* Content area on right */
.te-slide {
  position: relative;
}

.te-slide::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 58%;
  height: 100%;
  padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Token category badge */
.ts-category {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-3);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* Token number + name */
.ts-num {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.1vw, 18px);
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.ts-name {
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px);
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.ts-question {
  font-size: clamp(16px, 1.3vw, 20px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text-2);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

/* ILLUSTRATION */
.ts-illustration img {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  max-height: 500px;
  object-fit: contain;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(24,24,27,0.06);
}

/* Responsive: mobile stacks vertically */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .te-slide {
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: auto;
  }
  .te-slide > .ts-illustration {
    flex: none;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 400px;
    padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    order: -1;
  }
  .te-slide > *:not(.ts-illustration) {
    flex: none;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .te-slide::before {
    display: none;
  }
  /* Stack content vertically on mobile */
  .ts-category,
  .ts-num,
  .ts-name,
  .ts-question,
  .ts-values-label,
  .ts-values,
  .ts-desc {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0 clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
  }
  .ts-category:first-of-type {
    padding-top: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
  }
  .ts-desc {
    padding-bottom: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
  }
}

/* Token values — prominent */
.ts-values-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-3);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.ts-values {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.ts-val {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(12px, 0.9vw, 14px);
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 8px 18px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.12);
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}

/* Token description */
.ts-desc {
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 18px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.ts-desc strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

/* Arrow nav */
.te-arrows {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 32px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  z-index: 60;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.te-arrows.show { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }

.te-arrow-btn {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-2);
  transition: all 0.2s;
  font-family: var(--mono);
}
.te-arrow-btn:hover {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #fff;
  border-color: var(--accent);
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 4 — HOW IT WORKS (Interactive Demo)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#systems { background: var(--bg-cool); min-height: auto; padding-top: 60px; padding-bottom: 60px; }
.sys-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.sys-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 36px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.sys-sub {
  font-size: clamp(13px, 1vw, 16px);
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 580px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

/* Scenario picker */
.demo-scenarios {
  display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
}
.demo-scenario-btn {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text-2); cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s var(--ease);
}
.demo-scenario-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
.demo-scenario-btn.active {
  background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-color: var(--accent);
}

/* Demo container */
.demo-container {
  max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
}

/* Step 1: Intent bubble */
.demo-intent {
  text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: all 0.6s var(--ease);
}
.demo-intent.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.demo-intent-bubble {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--bg); border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 12px 24px;
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 20px); font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
}
.demo-intent-bubble em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
.demo-arrow-down {
  margin: 8px auto; width: 2px; height: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), rgba(37,99,235,0.1));
  position: relative;
}
.demo-arrow-down::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: -4px;
  width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--accent); opacity: 0.3;
}

/* Step 2: Token grid */
.demo-tokens {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) { .demo-tokens { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

.demo-token {
  background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 12px;
  cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.4s var(--ease);
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.95);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.demo-token.show {
  opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
}
.demo-token:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(37,99,235,0.08);
}
.demo-token.active {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.03);
}
.demo-token-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.demo-token-num {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;
}
.demo-token-name {
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px); font-weight: 500; color: var(--text);
}
.demo-token-value {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;
  padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 5px;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08); display: inline-block;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px);
  transition: all 0.4s var(--ease) 0.2s;
}
.demo-token.show .demo-token-value {
  opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0);
}

/* Token detail panel (click to expand) */
.demo-token-detail {
  max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.4s var(--ease), margin-top 0.3s;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.demo-token.active .demo-token-detail {
  max-height: 200px; margin-top: 10px;
}
.demo-token-rule {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7;
  padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--bg-cool);
  border-radius: 8px; border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
}
.demo-token-rule strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

/* Arrow between tokens and output */
.demo-arrow-center {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 6px; margin: 12px 0;
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.6s var(--ease);
}
.demo-arrow-center.show { opacity: 1; }
.demo-arrow-line {
  width: 30px; height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), var(--bg-dark));
}
.demo-arrow-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-3);
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* Step 3: Output card */
.demo-output {
  background: var(--bg-dark); border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 16px 20px; color: #fff;
  text-align: left; position: relative;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: all 0.6s var(--ease);
}
.demo-output.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.demo-output-label {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.demo-output-title {
  font-weight: 200; font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 22px);
  letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2;
}
.demo-output-features {
  display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.demo-output-feature {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(10px, 0.7vw, 12px);
  padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.demo-output-why {
  margin-top: 10px; font-size: clamp(12px, 0.85vw, 14px);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.5; font-style: italic;
}

/* Replay button */
.demo-replay {
  margin-top: 24px; text-align: center;
}
.demo-replay-btn {
  font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px;
  padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text-2); cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s var(--ease); letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.demo-replay-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   PHASE 5 — PROJECTS
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#projects {
  background: var(--bg);
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.projects-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(11px, 0.85vw, 13px);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.projects-title {
  font-weight: 200;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 48px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

>#projects .phase-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: start;
}
#projects .projects-label,
#projects .projects-title {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
}
.project-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 20px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
}
.project-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(24,24,27,0.06);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
.pc-num {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.pc-title {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.pc-subtitle {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-3); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0;
  display: none;
}
.pc-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-2); font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px;
  flex-grow: 1;
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.pc-tokens { display: none; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.pc-tag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(10px, 0.75vw, 12px);
  padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 6px;
  background: rgba(37,99,235,0.05);
  color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;
}
.pc-arrow { font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   NAV
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
.nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  height: 56px;
  background: rgba(220,225,232,0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(180%);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.5s var(--ease);
}
.nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  border-bottom-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}
.nav-inner {
  width: var(--max-w);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px);
}
.nav-logo { text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; }
.nav-logo-img { height: 22px; width: auto; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); }
.nav.scrolled .nav-logo-img { filter: none; }
.nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 28px); }
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s var(--ease);
}
.nav.scrolled .nav-links a { color: var(--text-3); }
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
.nav-links a[href="../framework/index.html"] { color: #fff; }
.nav.scrolled .nav-links a[href="../framework/index.html"] { color: var(--accent); }
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .nav-links a:not(.nav-cta) { display: none; }
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
   FOOTER
   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
.footer {
  background: var(--bg-dark);
  padding: 56px clamp(24px, 4vw, 64px);
  border-top: none;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.footer::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 400px;
  height: 400px;
  opacity: 0.02;
  background: url('../assets/logo/IF-lockup-white.svg') no-repeat center;
  background-size: 100%;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.footer-inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.footer-logo {
  height: 24px;
  width: auto;
  opacity: 0.3;
}
.footer a {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}
.footer a:hover {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,1);
}
.footer-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  justify-content: center;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .footer {
    padding: 44px 24px;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .footer-links {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
}

/* ═══ RESPONSIVE ═══ */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .phase { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .te-slide { padding: 24px 20px; min-height: calc(100vh - 56px); }
  .ts-name { font-size: 28px; }
  .footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="../index.html" class="nav-logo"><img src="../assets/logo/IF-lockup-black.svg" alt="intentFirst" class="nav-logo-img"></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="../framework/index.html">Tokens</a>
      <a href="../applied/index.html">Projects</a>
      <a href="../journal/index.html">Essays</a>
      <a href="../about/index.html">About</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 0 — HERO
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="phase" id="hero">
  <div class="phase-inner" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="hero-label">Context Grammar</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Intent becomes<br>the <em>interface.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Apps are disappearing. What replaces them? A system that reads your intent, your context, your constraints — and shapes itself in real time. The phone stops asking. It just knows.
    </p>
    <div class="scroll-cue">
      Scroll
      <div class="scroll-cue-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 1 — THE GAP
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="phase" id="gap">
  <div class="phase-inner">
    <h2 class="gap-section-title reveal">The 8 things your phone still can't read.</h2>
    <div class="gap-grid">

      <div class="gap-knows">
        <div class="gap-col-title reveal">What your phone already knows</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d1"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Your location (GPS)</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d2"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Current time</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d3"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Screen size & orientation</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d4"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Battery level</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d5"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Network connection</div>
      </div>

      <div class="gap-divider-v"></div>

      <div class="gap-misses">
        <div class="gap-col-title reveal">What it doesn't know — yet</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d1"><span class="gi-dot"></span> What you're trying to do</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d2"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Whether your hands are free</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d3"><span class="gi-dot"></span> How tired your brain is</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d4"><span class="gi-dot"></span> Who's watching your screen</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d5"><span class="gi-dot"></span> What matters most to you right now</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d6"><span class="gi-dot"></span> How much you trust the AI</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d6"><span class="gi-dot"></span> What other screens are nearby</div>
        <div class="gap-item reveal d6"><span class="gi-dot"></span> What's actually possible right now</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 2 — INTENT AT THE CENTER
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="phase" id="framework">
  <div class="phase-inner">

    <div class="intent-hub">
      <!-- Center: Intent -->
      <div class="intent-center reveal">
        <div class="intent-center-label">It starts with one thing</div>
        <h2 class="intent-center-title">You want <em>something.</em></h2>
        <p class="intent-center-sub">That's your intent. But to truly help you, AI needs to understand 7 more things about your world right now.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Connector -->
      <div class="intent-connector reveal d1">
        <div class="intent-connector-line"></div>
        <span class="intent-connector-label">AI asks 7 questions</span>
        <div class="intent-connector-line"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- 7 dimension cards (Intent is already stated above) -->
      <div class="dim-grid">
        <div class="dim-card reveal d2" data-token="1">
          <div class="dim-card-question">Can you use your hands?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Physical State</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Driving, one hand on a strap, cooking...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d2" data-token="2">
          <div class="dim-card-question">How tired is your brain?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Cognitive Load</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Focused, exhausted, panicking...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d3" data-token="3">
          <div class="dim-card-question">Who can see your screen?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Social Exposure</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Alone, crowded train, with family...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d3" data-token="4">
          <div class="dim-card-question">What matters most right now?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Priority Weight</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Speed vs. cost, safety vs. convenience...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d4" data-token="5">
          <div class="dim-card-question">How much do you trust the AI?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Synchro Rate</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Just suggest, auto-execute, somewhere between...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d4" data-token="6">
          <div class="dim-card-question">What screens are around you?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Form Factor</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">Phone only, TV nearby, car display...</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dim-card reveal d5" data-token="7">
          <div class="dim-card-question">What's actually possible right now?</div>
          <div class="dim-card-name">Feasibility</div>
          <div class="dim-card-examples">28 min to home, fridge half empty, store closed...</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fw-explore-hint reveal d6">↓ Click any card or scroll down to explore each one in detail</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 3 — TOKEN EXPLORER
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="explorer">

  <!-- Tab navigation -->
  <nav class="te-nav">
    <button class="te-tab active" data-i="0"><span class="te-tab-num">①</span>Intent</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="1"><span class="te-tab-num">②</span>Physical</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="2"><span class="te-tab-num">③</span>Cognitive</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="3"><span class="te-tab-num">④</span>Social</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="4"><span class="te-tab-num">⑤</span>Priority</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="5"><span class="te-tab-num">⑥</span>Synchro</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="6"><span class="te-tab-num">⑦</span>Form</button>
    <button class="te-tab" data-i="7"><span class="te-tab-num">⑧</span>Feasibility</button>
    <div class="te-progress">① of ⑧</div>
  </nav>

  <div class="te-slides">

    <!-- 01 Intent -->
    <div class="te-slide active" data-i="0">
      <div class="ts-category">Human Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">①</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Intent</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">What are you trying to do right now?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_01_Intent.jpg" alt="Intent illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Routine</span><span class="ts-val">Explore</span><span class="ts-val">Decide</span><span class="ts-val">Emergency</span><span class="ts-val">Create</span><span class="ts-val">Communicate</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Are you reordering your usual coffee, or frantically rebooking a canceled flight? The same app should look completely different based on what you're trying to do. Your intent can also <strong>shift mid-session</strong> — start browsing, end up buying.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 02 Physical State -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="1">
      <div class="ts-category">Human Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">②</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Physical State</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">Can you use your hands?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_02_PhysicalState.jpg" alt="Physical State illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Both Hands Free</span><span class="ts-val">One Hand</span><span class="ts-val">No Hands</span><span class="ts-val">Gloved</span><span class="ts-val">Walking</span><span class="ts-val">Driving</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">On the couch with both hands? Buttons can be small. Holding a train strap with one hand? Buttons get bigger. Driving? <strong>Voice only, no touch at all.</strong> Your body decides the interface.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 03 Cognitive Load -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="2">
      <div class="ts-category">Human Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">③</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Cognitive Load</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">How tired is your brain?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_03_ CognitiveLoad.jpg" alt="Cognitive Load illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Focused</span><span class="ts-val">Baseline</span><span class="ts-val">Divided</span><span class="ts-val">Depleted</span><span class="ts-val">Panic</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Focused? Show the full dashboard. Exhausted after work? Just two choices. <strong>Panicking? One button. The single best answer.</strong> Your mental energy decides how much the screen shows you.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 04 Social Exposure -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="3">
      <div class="ts-category">Human Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">④</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Social Exposure</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">Who can see your screen?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_04_SocialExposure.jpg" alt="Social Exposure illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Private</span><span class="ts-val">Public</span><span class="ts-val">Colleague</span><span class="ts-val">Family</span><span class="ts-val">Shared</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Alone? Show everything. Crowded train? <strong>Blur prices, silence notifications.</strong> With family? Split the screen — parents see prices and controls, kids see pictures and simple text.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 05 Priority Weight -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="4">
      <div class="ts-category">Control Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">⑤</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Priority Weight</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">What matters most right now?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_05_PriorityWeights.jpg" alt="Priority Weight illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Reliability > Cost</span><span class="ts-val">Feasibility > Variety</span><span class="ts-val">Privacy > Speed</span><span class="ts-val">Safety > Convenience</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Cheapest flight or most reliable one? When your needs conflict, <strong>something has to win</strong>. Designers set the default order. You can drag and reorder your priorities anytime.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 06 Synchro Rate -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="5">
      <div class="ts-category">Control Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">⑥</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Synchro Rate</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">How much should AI decide for you?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_06_SynchroRate.jpg" alt="Synchro Rate illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Suggest</span><span class="ts-val">Confirm</span><span class="ts-val">Notify</span><span class="ts-val">Autonomous</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Day one: you check everything. Six months later: you let it handle things. A dial with four positions — from <strong>"just suggest"</strong> to <strong>"do it automatically."</strong> Trust builds over time, and the dial moves with it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 07 Form Factor -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="6">
      <div class="ts-category">Human Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">⑦</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Form Factor</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">What screens are around you?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_07_FormFactor.jpg" alt="Form Factor illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">Phone Only</span><span class="ts-val">Phone + TV</span><span class="ts-val">Phone + Car</span><span class="ts-val">Phone + Watch</span><span class="ts-val">Lock Screen</span><span class="ts-val">Ambient</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">Just your phone? Full UI. TV nearby? <strong>Phone becomes a remote remote.</strong> In the car? Voice only. The phone shapeshifts based on what other screens are around it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 08 Feasibility -->
    <div class="te-slide" data-i="7">
      <div class="ts-category">Environment Token</div>
      <div class="ts-num">⑧</div>
      <h2 class="ts-name">Feasibility</h2>
      <p class="ts-question">What's actually possible right now?</p>
      <div class="ts-illustration"><img src="../assets/img/Small/Token_08_Feasibility.jpg" alt="Feasibility illustration"></div>
      <div class="ts-values-label">Token Values</div>
      <div class="ts-values">
        <span class="ts-val">GPS + Traffic</span><span class="ts-val">Smart Fridge</span><span class="ts-val">Purchase History</span><span class="ts-val">Calendar</span><span class="ts-val">Flight Data</span><span class="ts-val">Store Inventory</span>
      </div>
      <p class="ts-desc">28 minutes until you're home. Chicken and rice in the fridge. Supermarket is too far. <strong>Impossible options never appear.</strong> Only what you can actually do, right now, with what you have.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Arrow nav -->
  <div class="te-arrows" id="teArrows">
    <button class="te-arrow-btn" id="prevToken">←</button>
    <button class="te-arrow-btn" id="nextToken">→</button>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 4 — SYSTEMS VIEW
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="phase" id="systems">
  <div class="phase-inner" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="sys-label reveal">How It Works</div>
    <h2 class="sys-title reveal">All 8 tokens fire at once.<br>The interface reshapes itself.</h2>
    <p class="sys-sub reveal d1" style="margin:0 auto 48px;text-align:center;">
      Pick a scenario and watch Context Grammar decompose a single intent into 8 dimensions — then generate an interface that fits that exact moment.
    </p>

    <!-- Scenario selector -->
    <div class="demo-scenarios reveal d2">
      <button class="demo-scenario-btn active" data-scenario="0">What can I cook tonight?</button>
      <button class="demo-scenario-btn" data-scenario="1">It's raining</button>
      <button class="demo-scenario-btn" data-scenario="2">Find shoes, not puffy</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Interactive Demo -->
    <div class="demo-container">
      <!-- Intent bubble -->
      <div class="demo-intent" id="demoIntent">
        <div class="demo-intent-bubble" id="demoIntentText"></div>
        <div class="demo-arrow-down"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- 8 Token grid -->
      <div class="demo-tokens" id="demoTokens"></div>

      <!-- Arrow to output -->
      <div class="demo-arrow-center" id="demoArrow">
        <span class="demo-arrow-label">↓</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Output -->
      <div class="demo-output" id="demoOutput"></div>

      <!-- Replay -->
      <div class="demo-replay">
        <button class="demo-replay-btn" id="demoReplay">↻ Replay animation</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     PHASE 5 — PROJECTS
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="phase" id="projects" style="background:var(--bg)">
  <div class="phase-inner">
    <div class="projects-label reveal">3 Projects</div>
    <h2 class="projects-title reveal">Three different problems.<br>The same 8 tokens.</h2>

    <a class="project-card reveal d1" href="../applied/index.html#project-01">
      <div class="pc-num">PROJECT 01</div>
      <div class="pc-title">The Living Home</div>
      <div class="pc-subtitle">Samsung Ecosystem × Longitudinal Trust × Multi-Person Orchestration</div>
      <p class="pc-desc">A year later, you open the fridge and everything is there. You did nothing. AI learned your family's patterns, preferences, and rhythms across months — from manual grocery runs to fully automated household orchestration.</p>
      <div class="pc-tokens"><span class="pc-tag">⑤ Priority</span><span class="pc-tag">⑥ Synchro</span><span class="pc-tag">⑧ Feasibility</span></div>
      <div class="pc-arrow">Explore →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card reveal d2" href="../applied/index.html#project-02">
      <div class="pc-num">PROJECT 02</div>
      <div class="pc-title">The Family Trip</div>
      <div class="pc-subtitle">Multi-Phase Living Project × Crisis Management × Post-Trip Synthesis</div>
      <p class="pc-desc">Family of four. Two weeks in Japan. It rains in Kyoto — 10 seconds later, the entire itinerary restructures itself. Day 7, your son gets a fever. AI doesn't say "you can still go to Disney." It says "I can tell you by 8am tomorrow."</p>
      <div class="pc-tokens"><span class="pc-tag">① Intent</span><span class="pc-tag">⑧ Feasibility</span><span class="pc-tag">⑦ Form</span></div>
      <div class="pc-arrow">Explore →</div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card reveal d3" href="../applied/index.html#project-03">
      <div class="pc-num">PROJECT 03</div>
      <div class="pc-title">Fluid Handoff & Shared Arbitration</div>
      <div class="pc-subtitle">Intent Translation & Form Factor Transformation</div>
      <p class="pc-desc">Winter shoes for my son. Black, waterproof. But NOT puffy inside. No filter handles that. AI analyzes 300 reviews. On the platform: full browsing. On the train: one-handed cards. At home: phone becomes a remote, TV shows the grid. Your son points. You select. AI protects the moment of choosing together.</p>
      <div class="pc-tokens"><span class="pc-tag">② Physical</span><span class="pc-tag">④ Social</span><span class="pc-tag">⑦ Form</span></div>
      <div class="pc-arrow">Explore →</div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

